            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-300">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-academy-teal mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 01.143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 01-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 011.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 011.05-.143z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
