          </ul>
          <a href="#contact" class="block text-center px-6 py-3 bg-academy-teal text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-academy-teal-dark transition-colors">
            Inquire Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-16">Multi-day packs available — ask us about 5, 10, and 20-day packages for savings.</p>

      <!-- Add-Ons -->
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <span class="inline-block text-academy-teal text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Add-Ons</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-brand-charcoal mb-2">Make Their Day Even Better</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">Available for all daycare clients. Add any of these to your dog's visit.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.848 8.25l1.536.887M7.848 8.25a3 3 0 11-5.196-3 3 3 0 015.196 3zm1.536.887a2.165 2.165 0 011.083 1.839c.005.351.054.695.14 1.024M9.384 9.137l2.077 1.199m0 0a4.323 4.323 0 012.068-1.379l5.325-1.628a4.5 4.5 0 012.48-.044l.803.215-7.794 4.5m-2.882-1.664A4.331 4.331 0 0010.607 12m3.736 0l7.794 4.5-.802.215a4.5 4.5 0 01-2.48-.043l-5.326-1.629a4.324 4.324 0 01-2.068-1.379M14.343 12l-2.882 1.664" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-charcoal text-sm mb-1">Nail Trim</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Quick, stress-free nail trim</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-charcoal text-sm mb-1">Bath</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Fresh and clean at pickup</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-charcoal text-sm mb-1">Brush</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Coat brushing and grooming</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 11.25v8.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5 1.5H5.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5-1.5v-8.25M12 4.875A2.625 2.625 0 109.375 7.5H12m0-2.625V7.5m0-2.625A2.625 2.625 0 1114.625 7.5H12m0 0V21m-8.625-9.75h18c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125h-18c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v1.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-charcoal text-sm mb-1">Enrichment Treats</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Mental stimulation snacks</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-charcoal text-sm mb-1">Treadmill</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Controlled cardio session</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 p-5 text-center">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.362 5.214A8.252 8.252 0 0112 21 8.25 8.25 0 016.038 7.048 8.287 8.287 0 009 9.6a8.983 8.983 0 013.361-6.867 8.21 8.21 0 003 2.48z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-charcoal text-sm mb-1">Slatmill</h4>
