        <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 p-5 text-center sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-academy-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-academy-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.827 6.175A2.31 2.31 0 015.186 7.23c-.38.054-.757.112-1.134.175C2.999 7.58 2.25 8.507 2.25 9.574V18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h15A2.25 2.25 0 0021.75 18V9.574c0-1.067-.75-1.994-1.802-2.169a47.865 47.865 0 00-1.134-.175 2.31 2.31 0 01-1.64-1.055l-.822-1.316a2.192 2.192 0 00-1.736-1.039 48.774 48.774 0 00-5.232 0 2.192 2.192 0 00-1.736 1.039l-.821 1.316z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 12.75a4.5 4.5 0 11-9 0 4.5 4.5 0 019 0zM18.75 10.5h.008v.008h-.008V10.5z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-charcoal text-sm mb-1">Special Photo Days</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Themed photo sessions — holiday shoots, birthday paws, and more</p>
